Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent on cases involving Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION

Name: Average resolution time for cases with Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION before reaching Request Payment

Name: Total resolution time for cases with Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION before reaching Payment Handled

Name: Minimum time to reach Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION from the start of the case

Name: Average time it takes from Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION to the next activity in the process

Name: Total time from Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER in cases of multiple rejections
